---
title: Cheesy BBQ Chicken, Bacon & Corn Pizza with Fresh Dough & Caramelised Onion
description: Who needs takeaway when homemade can taste this good? This pizza topping combo takes first place - juicy BBQ chicken, bacon, caramelised onion and pops of sweet freshness from the sweetcorn. Add a double helping of Cheddar cheese for extra melty goodness, and you’re onto a winner!
